<p class="txtMainBlack">The <a href="/study-here/postgraduate-research-study/2024/phd/" title="Doctor of Philosophy (PhD)">Doctor of Philosophy (PhD)</a> is a degree awarded solely on the satisfactory completion of a supervised research project.</p>]]></Value>
